snippet.title: EnglishSimmer
snippet.description:
Hi there,

I enjoy procrastinating by playing The Sims and recording it for you guys to (hopefully) enjoy. Sometimes I even go as far as playing other games for entertainment. 
I am obliged to say that if you aren't subscribed already then you should.
